    {
      "title": "Solve for x",
      "content": "$$4x=20$$<br/>Divide both sides by 4: $$x=5$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Find y by substitution",
      "content": "$$-3x+y=-7$$<br/>Substitute $$x=5$$: $$-3(5)+y=-7$$<br/>Simplify: $$-15+y=-7$$<br/>Add 15 to both sides: $$y=8$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Compute x+y and select answer",
      "content": "$$x+y=5+8=13$$<br/>That matches choice C \u2014 <strong>C</strong> is correct."
